    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Here, we report the coding complete genome sequences of 23 severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2(SARS-CoV-2) strains from the Philippines. Sequences were obtained from nasopharyngeal and oropharyngeal swabs from COVID-19 positive patients. Mutation analysis showed the presence of the D614G mutation in the spike protein in 22 of 23 genomes.</jats:p>",
